B.Qu=new A.a4("If the fuel quantity drops below minimum, the aircraft must return to base.","Yak\u0131t miktar\u0131 minimumun alt\u0131na d\xfc\u015ferse u\xe7ak \xfcsse d\xf6nmelidir.","If the fuel quantity drops")
