B.Rk=new A.a4("Operations during the WOCL significantly increase the risk of crew error.","Sirkadiyen d\xfc\u015f\xfc\u015f penceresinde (02:00-06:00) operasyon, m\xfcrettebat hatas\u0131 riskini \xf6nemli \xf6l\xe7\xfcde art\u0131r\u0131r.","WOCL")
